{"title":"给孩子","authors":["江边"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你书桌上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排成一长溜的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《少年百科丛书》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不禁想起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己，贪婪地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阅读包装纸的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当我到副食店"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一角钱的咸菜，或者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两角钱的肉末儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在回家的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是一边走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边咀嚼着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包装纸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那新鲜而诱人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只言片语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今我仍记得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把印着《红楼梦》评论"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被咸菜濡湿的书叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小心地晾干、折起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍藏在心爱的日记本里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是这些食品包装纸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引起了我对文学的兴趣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管它们是那样寒酸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面总是沾满了污迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对在书堆中长大的你来说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许不值得一提"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的确"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在文化知识的某些方面，你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至可以当我的老师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是，孩子啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我却忧虑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个比书本更重要的问题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活中艰辛的一面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如何为你补起"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}